Transcript:
Agent: Hello, main Aryan hoon Trimfinity se. Maine dekha ki aapne product cart mein add kiya tha. Aaj ke din aapke liye additional 5% off hai. Kya aap ise claim karna chahenge?
Agent: "Hello ASWIN ji, lagta hai aap busy ho gaye the. Bas yaad dilana tha ki aapke cart mein Trimfinity 7000 Body and Ball Trimmer abhi bhi hai. Agar aapko koi bhi sawal ya confusion ho, toh mujhe bataiye. Waise, aaj ke liye ek exclusive 5% off ka offer bhi hai—code hai O-F-F-5. Aapko help karu checkout karne mein?"
